sg":"一直都覺得信星座嘅人係好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096fb44f6a3a8bfc454ceb33883001dac5c1e325","tid":128220,"uid":86373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星座撚語錄:<br />\n<br />\n「你咁理性 應該係山羊座/處女座 」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人類係應該要有理性架<br />\n如果依個世界得山羊座同處女座係理性思考(其實都唔係理性,而係簡單地用腦思考)<br />\n咁就大件事</blockquote><br />\n巴打我欣賞你 不過我都係翻去研究星座先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bdcdaeb649c6a38e5c8d460033edf38576a669","tid":128220,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:03:22.000Z","msg":"好似係年紀問題，係連登你可能同個小學生係同一個post吹緊水  <br />\n小學生就係傾星座ga la, 唔通傾AV咩<br />\n<br />\n利申 小學生"},{"pid":"7b8c5d1f28fb005c8bcf1890d49e72805bb33b24","tid":128220,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>星座撚語錄:<br />\n<br />\n「你咁理性 應該係山羊座/處女座 」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人類係應該要有理性架<br />\n如果依個世界得山羊座同處女座係理性思考(其實都唔係理性,而係簡單地用腦思考)<br />\n咁就大件事</blockquote><br />\n巴打我欣賞你 不過我都係翻去研究星座先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「有人說:占星學就是搞那些星座啊!!；<br />\n答：星座學是占星學中的一部份，但卻不是占星學的全貌。雖然太陽對我們來說是一顆非常重要的恆星，但星座學只討論太陽這個朋友有什麼樣的性格，以及當你出生時太陽因所處的黃道位置而產生投射上的質變，因此，如果完全忽略其他八個行星朋友以及與我們生活息息相關的衛星月亮，那麼不管是古典占星學或是現代心理占星學，在論述個人特質的基礎上顯然是完全不夠的。」<br />\n<br />\n依位同學,<br />\n星座本身無咩值得研究<br />\n真係對依方面有興趣就唔該去學下占星咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a770a9c5b212bf1bcb33f896a91a3e0f225e09","tid":128220,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cea8a3d58ecd39a67480ca813975f24f12b21ce","tid":128220,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"星座撚笑料:<br />\n<br />\n「雙魚男鍾意咩類型有冇人解答到<br />\n&gt;長曲髮<br />\n&gt;斯文 心地善良<br />\n&gt;見多你幾次 互動多幾下特別經歷就會自己亂諗 <br />\n&gt;&gt;討厭多咀狗/強詞奪理潑婦罵街」<br />\n<br />\n我諗依個世界應該除左雙魚男之外,所有人都唔會討厭多咀狗/強詞奪理潑婦罵街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw星座撚癲到連髮型都要限制埋<br />\n真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"82f3db60ec0faf53e82b7c79f040473a52acb737","tid":128220,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"不嬲都覺<br />\n但廢事比人話我撩交打<br />\n所以廢事理佢地<br />\nbtw識親d女講星座果d十居其九都係低能兒童"},{"pid":"9bbd7dd061ae7e8f96c72195b5d5b7a267314d86","tid":128220,"uid":62564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"其實樓主你自己都識得分清咩叫太陽星座<br />\n就知道最低階既星座撚淨係講太陽星座=全部<br />\n其實果班係真係屌都費閪事架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真正想了解占星既人都走左去正經學占星學<br />\n太陽星座只係占星學既百份之一都冇"},{"pid":"d088f62a8ee90a9dfdbf70ef7deaede660a450b2","tid":128220,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b88b0b52e4aaba957a0f10bcc0b08061c806fda3","tid":128220,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67510b9bc53d991209efe4684c259b90eba59af","tid":128220,"uid":45433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"我係射手，處女男朋友<br />\n<br />\n咁你同你男友遲早分手<br />\n你咁中意自由，又同咁多異性有咁好關係<br />\n加上